p <- counts_de %>%
    pivot_transcript() %>%

  # Subset data
    filter(!lowly_abundant) %>%
    mutate(significant = FDR<0.05 & abs(logFC) >=2) %>%

  # Plot
    ggplot(aes(x = logFC, y = PValue, label=feature)) +
    geom_point(aes(color = significant, size = significant, alpha=significant)) +
    geom_text_repel() +
